{"tid":485940,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Home Gaming/Web Server有咩分法可以做到？","createTime":"2017-12-01T11:42:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T08:41:47.000Z","uid":79546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5e2ca5f9323a6e7cac6ff50070727559bba04f8b","tid":485940,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T11:42:55.000Z","msg":"用NAS唔夠力推Gaming server<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nQnap TS Ryzen 5又貴到傻左<br />\n於是Plan好左6K Budget左右整部機仔放屋企<br />\nNevigator好似冇得比人係住宿申請Static IP<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a467889dd93affd28e6af0c84f14ec79b00e470","tid":485940,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T12:05:13.000Z","msg":"即係啲Game擺喺另一部機？"},{"pid":"ac9145e2851645f418828082c5bdadd032195998","tid":485940,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T13:12:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係啲Game擺喺另一部機？</blockquote><br />\n開Server，唔係Storage<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ea1ea5f65eb9a5662a5ae3f9d0163ac26b04fd","tid":485940,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T13:13:33.000Z","msg":"方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打錯咗"},{"pid":"ba83f2dd496da43b4f45e555dba7658b0b82b428","tid":485940,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T13:18:19.000Z","msg":"其實Dynamic IP Keep住唔Release咪得<br />\n再唔係平平哋買個Domain Name都得"},{"pid":"384e99d0652452dc4b7195f746a16808448de4f8","tid":485940,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T17:00:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實Dynamic IP Keep住唔Release咪得<br />\n再唔係平平哋買個Domain Name都得</blockquote><br />\n有諗過呢個方法,DDNS去做backup, 甩左就再揾翻IP RESET"},{"pid":"83e0d6da3e26fa0ce7c71012e2d0049226cfcac9","tid":485940,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T17:12:53.000Z","msg":"問題係呢度喇，本身就有個NAS port forward左80 443<br />\nModem就得兩個IP, 一個就上網比左NAS，一個就nowTV<br />\n上網睇就話即使Modem有4個RJ45頭，都只係會開兩個，要多個Dynamic IP就要拉多條光纖入嚟加modem"},{"pid":"9cf6a656465cf84a157795566962ed2baa955627","tid":485940,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T18:31:49.000Z","msg":"Modem直出畀NAS冇經Router？"},{"pid":"1e5c820d1da16df746e43af3e9eab86597d85d96","tid":485940,"uid":14346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T05:01:13.000Z","msg":"即係<br />\n[wan] <br />\n    | <br />\n[router] - [PC]<br />\n      | <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">80, 443</span><br />\n  [NAS]<br />\n<br />\n加多部細機仔做game server囉<br />\n個server大唔大咬？"},{"pid":"9d84e23d0eaf54cf58ac7a39bc50d442057a3780","tid":485940,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T05:02:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Modem直出畀NAS冇經Router？</blockquote><br />\n經左Router, 再Port forward"},{"pid":"865db32b3ea43f4bffddfdf2d2019e0b1a76b5a9","tid":485940,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T05:04:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係<br />\n[wan] <br />\n    | <br />\n[router] - [PC]<br />\n      | <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">80, 443</span><br />\n  [NAS]<br />\n<br />\n加多部細機仔做game server囉<br />\n個server大唔大咬？</blockquote><br />\n我就係想整多個web server + gaming server<br />\n但係個IP已經比NAS出左街，所以又要入多條線<br />\nServer都幾大咬，事關都想開50-100人Server"},{"pid":"e5d5a7795ad270e14861b72c54c29f3c7ade1812","tid":485940,"uid":14346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T05:09:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>即係<br />\n[wan] <br />\n    | <br />\n[router] - [PC]<br />\n      | <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">80, 443</span><br />\n  [NAS]<br />\n<br />\n加多部細機仔做game server囉<br />\n個server大唔大咬？</blockquote><br />\n我就係想整多個web server + gaming server<br />\n但係個IP已經比NAS出左街，所以又要入多條線<br />\nServer都幾大咬，事關都想開50-100人Server</blockquote><br />\n有冇domain?有就起部firewall用haproxy +  prefix射俾唔同機<br />\n冇就nas唔好用port80&amp;443放出街改其他port<br />\n或者用其中一個web server用80&amp;443對街做frontend，link啲contents去第二部機"},{"pid":"bfb5197315b8f1dd2643dfa25abcaa3dead247c1","tid":485940,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T05:18:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>即係<br />\n[wan] <br />\n    | <br />\n[router] - [PC]<br />\n      | <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">80, 443</span><br />\n  [NAS]<br />\n<br />\n加多部細機仔做game server囉<br />\n個server大唔大咬？</blockquote><br />\n我就係想整多個web server + gaming server<br />\n但係個IP已經比NAS出左街，所以又要入多條線<br />\nServer都幾大咬，事關都想開50-100人Server</blockquote><br />\n有冇domain?有就起部firewall用haproxy +  prefix射俾唔同機<br />\n冇就nas唔好用port80&amp;443放出街改其他port<br />\n或者用其中一個web server用80&amp;443對街做frontend，link啲contents去第二部機</blockquote><br />\n跟qnap domain，因為屋企有電腦白痴，唔識用8080入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上我放web唔想比人入到個NAS WebUI <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec499839649e3ec5a0dd7767361faedd29ca0a5","tid":485940,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T05:19:56.000Z","msg":"明白太多限制，所以想集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51be143d01b6ba84add72f9d439861b0eb5b80c2","tid":485940,"uid":14346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T05:28:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>即係<br />\n[wan] <br />\n    | <br />\n[router] - [PC]<br />\n      | <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">80, 443</span><br />\n  [NAS]<br />\n<br />\n加多部細機仔做game server囉<br />\n個server大唔大咬？</blockquote><br />\n我就係想整多個web server + gaming server<br />\n但係個IP已經比NAS出左街，所以又要入多條線<br />\nServer都幾大咬，事關都想開50-100人Server</blockquote><br />\n有冇domain?有就起部firewall用haproxy +  prefix射俾唔同機<br />\n冇就nas唔好用port80&amp;443放出街改其他port<br />\n或者用其中一個web server用80&amp;443對街做frontend，link啲contents去第二部機</blockquote><br />\n跟qnap domain，因為屋企有電腦白痴，唔識用8080入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上我放web唔想比人入到個NAS WebUI <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係冇domain，得qnap個DDNS service<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋唔係好明<br />\n部nas個port80同443係web server定nas個webui?<br />\n同埋屋企人access部nas係去web server定webui?(定samba呢啲？)"},{"pid":"a3af1822863ed45185570a6329f06667169bf654","tid":485940,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T06:28:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>即係<br />\n[wan] <br />\n    | <br />\n[router] - [PC]<br />\n      | <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">80, 443</span><br />\n  [NAS]<br />\n<br />\n加多部細機仔做game server囉<br />\n個server大唔大咬？</blockquote><br />\n我就係想整多個web server + gaming server<br />\n但係個IP已經比NAS出左街，所以又要入多條線<br />\nServer都幾大咬，事關都想開50-100人Server</blockquote><br />\n有冇domain?有就起部firewall用haproxy +  prefix射俾唔同機<br />\n冇就nas唔好用port80&amp;443放出街改其他port<br />\n或者用其中一個web server用80&amp;443對街做frontend，link啲contents去第二部機</blockquote><br />\n跟qnap domain，因為屋企有電腦白痴，唔識用8080入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上我放web唔想比人入到個NAS WebUI <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係冇domain，得qnap個DDNS service<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋唔係好明<br />\n部nas個port80同443係web server定nas個webui?<br />\n同埋屋企人access部nas係去web server定webui?(定samba呢啲？)</blockquote><br />\nSorry 講到一舊舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nNAS port 80, 443 係webUI"},{"pid":"3f613e8ee1a972ad9e5f64f2ce2c7b98a9a98aff","tid":485940,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T11:40:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>即係<br />\n[wan] <br />\n    | <br />\n[router] - [PC]<br />\n      | <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">80, 443</span><br />\n  [NAS]<br />\n<br />\n加多部細機仔做game server囉<br />\n個server大唔大咬？</blockquote><br />\n我就係想整多個web server + gaming server<br />\n但係個IP已經比NAS出左街，所以又要入多條線<br />\nServer都幾大咬，事關都想開50-100人Server</blockquote><br />\n有冇domain?有就起部firewall用haproxy +  prefix射俾唔同機<br />\n冇就nas唔好用port80&amp;443放出街改其他port<br />\n或者用其中一個web server用80&amp;443對街做frontend，link啲contents去第二部機</blockquote><br />\n跟qnap domain，因為屋企有電腦白痴，唔識用8080入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上我放web唔想比人入到個NAS WebUI <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係冇domain，得qnap個DDNS service<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋唔係好明<br />\n部nas個port80同443係web server定nas個webui?<br />\n同埋屋企人access部nas係去web server定webui?(定samba呢啲？)</blockquote><br />\nSorry 講到一舊舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nNAS port 80, 443 係webUI</blockquote><br />\n屋企人係去webUI"},{"pid":"5558e1da1872e9d834cc2de049ad8ef3db5c700a","tid":485940,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T14:09:02.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb38a3b960f7be7d38e6e6b92795d8cc61b83a94","tid":485940,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T15:21:14.000Z","msg":"如果NAS個WebUI唔放出街點解要做Port Forwarding？"},{"pid":"177ce0a7c3a55be76c1ae3698da4bdb87800b659","tid":485940,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T15:53:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果NAS個WebUI唔放出街點解要做Port Forwarding？</blockquote><br />\n放出街呀，唔放冇得用DDNS"},{"pid":"a28c7f56cb5db6963845f5e20624e71150ec2262","tid":485940,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T15:56:47.000Z","msg":"其實我應該揾到解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2x1000 plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實依家成件事係<br />\nIP 1 同 IP 2<br />\nIP 1 就比NAS, 用左Port 80, 443 有DDNS 完全冇問題<br />\nIP 2就係比nowTV，但就唔足速度<br />\n所以最後都應該係要開多條線，連Router 再入server"},{"pid":"e25f97ae20d1974f392839d8ccf6645fd416a468","tid":485940,"uid":14346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:30:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我應該揾到解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2x1000 plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實依家成件事係<br />\nIP 1 同 IP 2<br />\nIP 1 就比NAS, 用左Port 80, 443 有DDNS 完全冇問題<br />\nIP 2就係比nowTV，但就唔足速度<br />\n所以最後都應該係要開多條線，連Router 再入server</blockquote><br />\n不如試下將部now tv插去部router後邊<br />\n都work嘅話成件事簡單好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847003767a6f3fac3ea0eecba4c7802acf7400ef","tid":485940,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T08:41:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實我應該揾到解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2x1000 plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實依家成件事係<br />\nIP 1 同 IP 2<br />\nIP 1 就比NAS, 用左Port 80, 443 有DDNS 完全冇問題<br />\nIP 2就係比nowTV，但就唔足速度<br />\n所以最後都應該係要開多條線，連Router 再入server</blockquote><br />\n不如試下將部now tv插去部router後邊<br />\n都work嘅話成件事簡單好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁咪全屋電腦電話都慢哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}